name: Soimah Pancawati
description: '''Soimah Pancawati''' (born 29 September 1980) is an Indonesian comedian, singer, [[pesindhèn]], and presenter from [[Yogyakarta]], [[Indonesia]]. She sings in several genres, including [[campursari]], [[pesindhèn]], [[ketoprak]], [[pop music|Java pop]], [[hip-hop]], and [[:id:dagelan|dagelan]]. She grew up in a coast village at [[:id:Tayu, Pati|Tayu, Pati]], [[Central Java]].
